snippet.title: Final Fantasy II (WonderSwan) - Part 1 - FRIONIEL!?  You Don't Hear That Everyday.
snippet.description: What kind of name IS that?  Well, I also show the ultimate technique for grinding skill, stat and weapon levels....put all the weapons on your "bad" hands, unequip all armor, and only cast spells IN battle, to increase the magic stat.
